title: Phish - 2004-06-26 - Alpine Valley Music Theatre [FLAC]
description:
06/26/2004	Alpine Valley Music Theatre, East Troy, WI

Set 1: Access Me[1] > Scents and Subtle Sounds[2], Stash, The Moma Dance, Divided Sky, Wilson > Funky Bitch > Character Zero

Set 2: Boogie On Reggae Woman -> Ghost > Free, Friday > Piper > Harry Hood

Encore: Possum

[1] Debut.
[2] No intro.

Noteworthy Jams: Free (highly recommended), Boogie On Reggae Woman (highly recommended), Ghost, Piper

Notes: This show marked the debut of Access Me. Scents did not contain the intro. During an especially long break before Stash, Trey joked that if they take longer between songs, but play the same amount of songs, the show would last longer.
